{"tid":2242804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"塔利班表態支持川普後 美軍即時空襲塔利班據點","createTime":"2020-10-14T09:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T12:08:46.000Z","uid":253829,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b82bfa0739f78543157b64f0a7e1e8824f30ae99","tid":2242804,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:27:22.000Z","msg":"美國軍方發言人表示，過去幾天，美軍在阿富汗西南部赫曼德省(Helmand Province)的塔利班據點發動空襲，這是塔利班在表態支持川普後，美軍所做的回應。<br />\n<br />\n上週末，塔利班發言人穆賈希德（Zabihullah Mujahid）表示，他們希望美國總統川普能夠連任，因為川普已承諾從阿富汗撤軍。但顯然川普團隊很不喜歡塔利班的聲援，川普公關組長莫托（Tim Murtaugh）發表聲明「我們拒絕塔利班的支持，塔利班應該知道，美國總統會以各種手段保護美國的利益。」<br />\n<br />\n就在川普團隊拒絕塔利班的支持後沒多久，美國空軍對塔利班陣地發動空襲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201013004565-260417?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201013004565-260417%3Fchdtv&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2mWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=21ea763b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201013004565-260417?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"f02e451aff1647f01e072821f16534647a76d0c0","tid":2242804,"uid":201604,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:29:04.000Z","msg":"幾時空襲埋香港恐怖份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c44269d4d3a7c4d2db62ecbe692647d3c3c3d8","tid":2242804,"uid":27432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"中國識玩"},{"pid":"a286bf21275f68b055f71accf4c58ca4e345f434","tid":2242804,"uid":245849,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"塔利班係中共正式接見正式會議嘅正式盟友，明顯係度玩嘢"},{"pid":"9315432b025f834e66bc70a65bc41b1ba93d8d1a","tid":2242804,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"支持你都比你炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁搞法，塔利班肯定更加